Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}迷子の感情抱きしめて眠っても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:42.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}後悔全然全然全然消えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:46.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}独りきりで首絞め合い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:50.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}完全聖人になんてなれやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつも理想に挫折して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:56.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自分責めるポーズだけとって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:00.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}お安い免罪握りしめて甘えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何遍失敗して直りもしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:06.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}反省ばかりで変われなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:09.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}心殺しやり過ごす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:13.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}終わらない懺悔と憂鬱の夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:22.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}完全な自分がどこにもいない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}最低な自分しか見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:10.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}成为不了完全的圣人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:17.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论失败几次都改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:21.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无药可救了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为就是做不到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:26.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}说着不该是这样的 逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:30.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}又想要一了百了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:33.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}讨厌这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:34.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}封闭自己自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:36.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}受伤 哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}即便抱着迷路羔羊的感情入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:42.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}后悔也完全完全完全无法释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:46.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}独自不断的钻着牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:50.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}成为不了完全的圣人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}理想总是事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:56.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只准备好自责的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:00.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}寻求着那廉价的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论失败几次都改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:06.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}虚心接受屡教不改
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:09.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}昧着良心得过且过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:13.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}没有尽头的忏悔与忧郁的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:22.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}没有完美的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只有最差劲的自己
Comment: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,========================ED==================================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}始まりはただの恋心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}気づけば唯一無二の拠り所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}同じ時刻み　齢をとろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}これからは　お願いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}stay with me stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:13.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}so long time 隣りにいて　永久に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:17.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}闘いの日々に疲れても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}怒りの雨に降られても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}濡れてしまうならば迷わず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}俺が代わりにあなたの傘となる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}寒くないよ　隣にいる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}ただそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}君は僕の拠り所さ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}その笑顔にまた癒やされる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}世界中　探しても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}代わりなんていない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}君は僕の拠り所さ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:48.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}そこにいるだけでまた満たされる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}どんなに傷ついても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}この身捧げ守るから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}最初不过是单纯的小小恋心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不觉间却成了我唯一的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}让我们在岁月中一同刻下年华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}今后也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}stay with me stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:13.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}so long time 永远在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:17.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不论是历战的疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}还是暴风雨的侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}当你脆弱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}我将毫不犹豫地为你遮风挡雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}只要你在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}就不会感到寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}你就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}总能被你的微笑治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}就算寻遍整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}也没有谁能代替你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}你就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:48.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}在你身边就是我最大的满足
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不管受怎样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}我都将舍身相护
